Description: Incorporates colour gradients from the 'cpt-city' web archive
    available at <https://phillips.shef.ac.uk/pub/cpt-city/>. Provides
    functions to search, preview, and return colour palettes as either
    interpolated hex vectors or colorRampPalette functions for use with
    base graphics, ggplot2, and sf.
